    tables (&lt;<a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table">table</a>&gt;), …</i>
&lt;/<a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article">article</a>&gt;</pre>
  </article>

