  <article>
    <header><h3>Figures</h3></header>

    <p>Use the following code to insert a figure:</p>

    <pre>&lt;<a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/figure">figure</a>&gt;
  <i>Figure contents:
